<s> The MSDOS console doesn't expand wildcards before calling programs.  </s>
<s> In principle Tidy could include the code for doing this for DOS, but I haven't gotten around to that.  </s>
<s> A workaround is to run tidy from within a script.  </s>
<s> You might place your text in comments, but HTML Tidy is designed for tidying HTML and not text files with odd bits of markup.  </s>
